    <h1>Welcome to your one-stop-dot for all your emotional and physical wellbeing.</h1>

    <p> posilivity is an online diary, which not only tracks your mental wellbeing but also syncs this to data collected from your fitbit to also log key information such as your weight, heartrate, sleeping patterns and excercise, by combining this data we will help you establish any patterns behind negative thoughts and actions and ways to address these. </p>

    <p>We also have a number of spealisist options for people who are trying to overcome depression, give up smoking and for people trying to control their stress for events such as exams.</p>

    <p> Our premium members will also benefit from flexible on-demand councellors who offer their services through FaceTime, one-to-one meetings or even whatsApp or messenger, whichever is easiest or best for you. </p>
