    <h1> Need advice?</h1>
    <p> You may have started to notice a pattern emerging in your behaviour. If this is so we advise you make an appointment with one of our councellors, who will analyse your data and discuss you emotions and feelings with you before advising you on the best next steps, whether this is talking to your GP or small changes (such as getting a SAD lamp) that might help. Our councellors are availiable 6 days a week between 8am and 7pm, however if you are in desparate need for help the following places will be able to help 24 hours a day 7 days a week.
    <ul>
      <li>The Samiritans</li>
      <li> CALM - for men aged 15-35</li>
      <li> Aniexty </li>
      <li> Depression Alliance</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
